# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Vendored @freshon/api SDK — its compiled dist MUST be tracked so it ships
# with the standalone/subtree clone (the `dist` rule above would otherwise drop it).
!vendor/freshon-api/dist/
!vendor/freshon-api/dist/**

